spec_data.Name: python-which
spec_data.Description:
which.py is a small which replacement. It has the following features:

 * it can print all matches on the PATH;
 * it can note "near misses" on the PATH (e.g. files that match but
   may not, say, have execute permissions); and
 * it can be used as a Python module.
spec_data.Signature: RSA/SHA256, Sat 29 Jul 2017 05:11:09 AM EDT, Key ID f55e7430f5282ee4
spec_data.Summary: Small which replacement that can be used as a Python module
